title: AVGN Collection 01 - 52 + The repotage from Gametrailers and the
description:
Here is my collection of the Angry Video Game Nerd movies (01 - 52) + A repotage from Gametrailers and the Remix of the AVGN Theme song from Dudelstudio.



I appologies for the bad quality of some of the movies because it was pretty hard to find it in good quality.


All of the Episodes are playable in VLC.


Enjoy!




P.S. Please seed when you are done ^_^
